# Insulin Glargine U-300

## Overview

Concentrated long-acting basal insulin formulation providing ultra-long 36-hour duration with reduced glycemic variability.

## Structure

| Property | Value |
| -------- | ----- |
| Name     | Insulin Glargine U-300 |

## Mechanism of Action

Gly-A21, Gly-B31-B32 modification causes isoelectric precipitation at physiological pH forming subcutaneous depot; U-300 concentration provides slower, more stable absorption.

